- Ensure success icon and "Legally signed" badges use status colors; buttons use primary accent #0052CC for primary CTAs.
- Use card design with #FFFFFF background, subtle shadow, 8–12px border-radius, and #E5E7EB dividers.
- Buttons: rounded rectangles, medium size; primary filled #0052CC with white text; secondary outline with muted text (#6B7280).
- Ensure adequate hit-target sizes (>=44px) for mobile CTAs and accessible color contrast.

